Package com.fortify.util.rest.webtarget

This package contains interfaces and implementations for updating WebTarget instances, for example adding a path or request parameters to an existing WebTarget instance.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IWebTargetUpdater
    This interface allows for updating WebTarget instances, for example by adding a path or query parameters.
    IWebTargetUpdaterBuilder
    Implementations of this interface allow for building IWebTargetUpdater instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WebTargetPathUpdater
    This IWebTargetUpdater implementation allows for appending paths (as configured through the constructor) to a given WebTarget instance.
    WebTargetPathUpdaterBuilder
    IWebTargetUpdaterBuilder implementation for building WebTargetPathUpdater instances.
    WebTargetQueryParamUpdater
    This IWebTargetUpdater implementation allows for adding a query parameter (as configured through the constructor) to a given WebTarget instance.
    WebTargetQueryParamUpdaterBuilder
    IWebTargetUpdaterBuilder implementation for building WebTargetQueryParamUpdater instances.
    WebTargetTemplateResolver
    This IWebTargetUpdater implementation allows for resolving template values in WebTarget instances.
    WebTargetTemplateResolverBuilder
    IWebTargetUpdaterBuilder implementation for building WebTargetTemplateResolver instances.
    WebTargetUpdaterBuilder
    This IWebTargetUpdaterBuilder implementation simply wraps an existing IWebTargetUpdater instance, and returns this instance when the WebTargetUpdaterBuilder.build() method is called.

Package com.fortify.util.rest.webtarget Description

This package contains interfaces and implementations for updating WebTarget instances, for example adding a path or request parameters to an existing WebTarget instance. In general, IWebTargetUpdater implementations should be immutable; corresponding IWebTargetUpdaterBuilder implementations can be used to build such IWebTargetUpdater instances.
